      <title>租赁巨头 Avolon 将收购 Castlelake，新增 118 架飞机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/leasing-giant-avolon-add-118-aircraft-with-castlelake-acquisition-2024-09-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰租赁巨头 Avolon 已同意收购规模较小的竞争对手 Castlelake Aviation Limited，从而增加包括 118 架飞机在内的 50 亿美元资产组合，这家全球第二大飞机租赁商周五表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/leasing-giant-avolon-add-118-aircraft-with-castlelake-acquisition-2024-09-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 15:29:46 GMT</pubDate>
